{"tid":656560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掛「反攻大陸」肩帶  GQ編輯總監被炒","createTime":"2018-05-07T10:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T11:52:37.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75c9fb4ddafd2ebc52bac21751d7b8e5164b3653","tid":656560,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/05/07/212753/i_336x255_022184870.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F212753%2Fi_336x255_022184870.jpg&h=7ea80811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">■杜祖業在歡送會上戴「反攻大陸」肩帶，與同事合照。</span><br />\n梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（星島日報報道）時尚雜誌《GQ》台灣版總編輯杜祖業，原定接任大陸版GQ（《智族GQ》）編輯總監，近日卻因「個人原因」而不被聘用。據了解，杜祖業被臨時撤換的原因，起於在台灣GQ舉辦的歡送會中，背上一條由同事製作的「反攻大陸」綬帶，因而挑動大陸敏感的民族主義神經。<br />\n<br />\n　　《GQ》（Gentlemen's Quarterly）是美國出版集團康泰納仕（COND&Eacute; NAST）旗下的男性時尚雜誌，大陸版的GQ創刊於二○○九年，因與官方中國新聞社合作，使用中新社旗下的「智族」刊號，因此成為《智族GQ》。<br />\n<br />\n　　北京智族雜誌社五月四日發出文件，任命編輯副總監曾鳴為《智族GQ》編輯總監，「杜祖業因其個人原因不被聘用」。據社交媒體流傳的照片，杜祖業的GQ台灣同事日前在歡送會上，別出心裁地為他準備了一條寫着「反攻大陸」的藍色綬帶，這個原為玩笑的創意，可能犯了大忌。台媒報道，在《智族GQ》的高層眼中，擔心它會為公司帶來類似「萬豪酒店爭議」的公關危機，於是在短短二十四小時內「快刀斬亂麻」。<br />\n<br />\n　　中央社引述大陸媒體界人士說，「智族GQ」雖然是時尚雜誌，非關政治，但相關事項也要符合規範，「反攻大陸」在台灣可能是一句無傷大雅的玩笑話，但若要來大陸就業，這麼說話就太沒有政治警覺性了。<br />\n<br />\n　　台灣陸委會拒就事件評論，但稱近期大陸對政治思想箝制，已達到無限上綱、任意指控的程度，因言獲罪案件屢見不鮮，呼籲民眾赴陸就學、就業，務必做好各項風險評估，保障自身權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1796828&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1796828%26target%3D2&d=N2JbAIWa9%2FbI8JrruRbENr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0d800c68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1796828%26target%3D2&h=59c6a418\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1796828&amp;target=2</a>"},{"pid":"8a5196a1ab48fbe7b6ac0879536684d823f3aa92","tid":656560,"uid":18251,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送比佢個位同事係咪代替左佢呀"},{"pid":"dd3e2475c124881e5541af53d2e799ce4b5c5b97","tid":656560,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"同去朝鮮風險一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5202dd967892f0051e5f5dd95c159e80a0b3bf","tid":656560,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a4eaccffb3ac8d28ff54a5294065de8ef59f1b","tid":656560,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"個同事咁撚仆街嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837da103cbeb4ebc42c51bcb190d8c713dccea9c","tid":656560,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"支那心"},{"pid":"5eee10ec489cd6db47538c11f2a2a65196b4268e","tid":656560,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a5196a1ab48fbe7b6ac0879536684d823f3aa92","tid":656560,"uid":18251,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送比佢個位同事係咪代替左佢呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"有預謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de21c022e46bbdedf60263ce11ec741f6fafa6f4","tid":656560,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"明知支那狗崩口人忌崩口碗，<br />\n要去賺支那錢就自己醒少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa